name: minnesota-school-district-and-attendance-boundaries-sy2008-2009
notes: This file represents the boundaries of all public school districts and school attendance areas in the state of Minnesota for school year 2008-2009. Each year Minnesota school districts report any changes to their elementary, middle and high school attendance area boundaries. This school district attendance file is maintained at the Minnesota Department of Education, but is also supplied to the State of Minnesota Legislative Coordinating Commission and the Land Management Information Center (LMIC).
